{"tid":1232952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（請廣傳）請唔好誣蔑烈士了","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:25:41.000Z","uid":162864,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de503bb54aa1c15cfa0302b3f717e7c1ce076882","tid":1232952,"uid":162864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"有朋友識烈士，烈士係佢舊校社工：<br />\n<br />\n我識嘅梁凌杰（梁sir），佢好多野都敢做，所有野有經過思考去做。<br />\n佢7年前係做社工，之後就無左聯繫<br />\n<br />\n大約喺我初中個年，曾經見到梁sir為左保護學生安全，差點連命都無。<br />\n<br />\n嗰次去camp，係全班一齊去，仲有梁sir都一齊嚟。嗰到有一個泰山蠅，有個同學都未聽專業人士講，就覺得自己好聰明咁搖到對面。但佢失去平衡，準備跌落去個磚頭個陣，梁sir跑過去攬住佢，就咁用身體保護個同學，自己就頭部流血入院。<br />\n<br />\n佢好多時候都係唔理自己就去理別人。有次明明係個同學錯嘅，但係梁sir都會同個老師講，去幫佢求情。<br />\n<br />\n佢係一個好社工，烈士，真香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你班仆街唔好再加鹽加醋"},{"pid":"6ce81b2d4f136797390e90287330ddc48105e0be","tid":1232952,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\nR.I.P."},{"pid":"adfd8f7a72a2b4cd802d4b377269779eedca876d","tid":1232952,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"烈士安息"},{"pid":"f458d1b6d6c08e6f64fcc989099ed15f1dc45e14","tid":1232952,"uid":50663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話烈士係真漢子咩？"},{"pid":"1414b6420e5d2d031cb86466ca075891b0ba9846","tid":1232952,"uid":162864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f458d1b6d6c08e6f64fcc989099ed15f1dc45e14","tid":1232952,"uid":50663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話烈士係真漢子咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"我都係幫朋友推 有待確認"}]}